title: WEDNESDAY 1/13 - Jackson a no-go on snow!
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 1/13 - Jackson a no-go on snow!
description:
The Rams and Packers (0:07) preparing for their NFC Divisional matchup as Aaron Rodgers knows he'll have his hands full with Aaron Donald (0:24). Lamar Jackson set to face the Bills in a snowy Buffalo, but Jackson says he's never played in snow before 1:25). We have the lastest news in coaching jobs including Eric Bieniemy (2:20) and Robert Saleh (2:39) plus the Seahawks looking for a new offensive coordinator (3:06) and the Chuck Pagano calls it a career in Chicago (3:33)
